Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.49,0:01:52.89,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}願い事　揺れる音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.01,0:01:55.89,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そっとひそめる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.20,0:02:03.07,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}頬のそばで舞う雪達…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.19,0:02:10.16,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}たくさんの後悔　過去を結ぶ笑顔たち
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.25,0:02:13.40,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}北風のささやき
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.51,0:02:16.52,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}触れて溶ける
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.87,0:02:24.18,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}冬空の淋しさを重ねて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:32.91,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}優しさの瞳越えて　今
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.95,0:02:40.14,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}伝えたいメロディ　指差した一番星光る空に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.25,0:02:48.44,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}描き集めた未来　かじかんだ指の隙間通る星座たち
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.63,0:02:56.60,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Ah　この場所から見た景色　叶えたい…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.79,0:03:02.46,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}約束ね
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------OPCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.49,0:01:52.89,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心中的願望  搖曳的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.01,0:01:55.89,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}悄悄隱藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.20,0:02:03.07,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}讓飛雪滑過臉頰…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.19,0:02:10.16,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}揮之不去的後悔  緊繫過去的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.25,0:02:13.40,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}北風的細語
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.51,0:02:16.52,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一觸即散
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.87,0:02:24.18,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}寒空中夾雜著寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:32.91,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}越過了眼中的溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.95,0:02:40.14,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}現在想給你的旋律  遙指著初星的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.25,0:02:48.44,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}天空拼湊出的未來  手指間露出的星座
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.63,0:02:56.60,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}啊  想要實現在此看見的景色…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.79,0:03:02.46,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}約定好了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------EDJP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.27,0:22:22.56,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}揺れる水面　その深くに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.05,0:22:26.22,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}青い宇宙映ってたね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.33,0:22:29.77,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}未来…そしてまた散っていく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.17,0:22:33.88,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}季節覚えている？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.37,0:22:41.44,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}私たちは運命紡ぎながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.95,0:22:46.70,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その糸がどこまで続いてくのか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.91,0:22:50.49,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}知らないままで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.04,0:22:51.42,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs17}(ただそこに)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.22,0:22:54.61,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}inspiration　喜びとか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.99,0:22:58.27,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}言葉を分かち合うたび
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.53,0:23:02.08,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ああいつか終わりの日が来る
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.28,0:23:05.84,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}そう感じさせるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.01,0:23:09.77,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}initialize　その扉を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.05,0:23:13.36,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}開ける時が来るのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.62,0:23:17.15,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}綺麗な時を閉じ込めて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.42,0:23:20.93,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}湖に沈めたの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.17,0:23:24.71,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}だけど私平気だよと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.93,0:23:30.35,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}星の便りに綴る
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------EDCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.27,0:22:22.56,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在漣漪的水面深處
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.05,0:22:26.22,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}照映著蔚藍的宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.33,0:22:29.77,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}未來又將飄零而去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.17,0:22:33.88,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}唯此季節長存心中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.37,0:22:41.44,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我們編織命運之絲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.95,0:22:46.70,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}卻從來都不曾知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.91,0:22:50.49,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}這絲線將通向何處
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.04,0:22:51.42,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs17}(僅僅佇立於此)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.22,0:22:54.61,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}每當我與他人分享
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.99,0:22:58.27,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}靈感乍現時的喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.53,0:23:02.08,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}就已經隱約察覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.28,0:23:05.84,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終會有結束的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.01,0:23:09.77,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}重置人生的那扇門
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.05,0:23:13.36,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終有漸漸打開之時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.62,0:23:17.15,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}美好時光關入其中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.42,0:23:20.93,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}再慢慢地沉入湖底
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.17,0:23:24.71,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不過我會在星星上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.93,0:23:30.35,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}寫下一句「我沒事」
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------PREV-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.30,0:00:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  還沒到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.62,0:00:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.52,0:00:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.29,0:00:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.76,0:00:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經說過好多遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.25,0:00:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.35,0:00:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.75,0:00:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怎麼記得
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.19,0:00:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時乃乃香還小  也是沒辦法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.18,0:00:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟那個時候比起來  小鎮也變樣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.66,0:00:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會嚇一跳的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.07,0:01:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像…假的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.02,0:01:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTA-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.17,0:03:12.96,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)\pos(50,270)}「飛碟小鎮」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下等下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.88,0:03:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦  安靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.14,0:03:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡  放去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.24,0:03:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知把電池取出來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.69,0:03:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看…我看…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.85,0:03:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這是爸爸的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.11,0:04:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七年了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.49,0:04:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.78,0:04:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  睡得好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拆行李的時候不小心睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.48,0:04:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長途跋涉嘛  也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.09,0:04:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒吃早飯吧  我現在去做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.89,0:04:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是昨天把食材都買好就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這個可以用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.55,0:04:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.71,0:04:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.07,0:04:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天說好的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.70,0:04:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.09,0:05:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頂住了哦  小春
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手多出來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外我可不是客人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.54,0:05:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳家沒店員了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.19,0:05:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  我是看板娘嘛  這些事情應該做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.95,0:05:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看板娘可不是負責看板的意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.38,0:05:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換我來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  湊太
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個飛碟饅頭跟以前吃過的溫泉饅頭有什麼區別
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外形吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.23,0:06:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那個東西  妳也是夠嗆的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.15,0:06:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有呢  因為它客人增多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟客人們聊天  好開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明難得的暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.30,0:06:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從小就在店裡幫忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.17,0:06:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那個時候開始  的確變了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  我就快洗完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後分頭進行大掃除
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.20,0:07:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就要去？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  說是今天無論如何都要交接好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.34,0:07:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想晚上就能回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  掃除呢  購物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就拜託妳啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人的話我才不會幹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.13,0:07:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會如你所願呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.52,0:07:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.79,0:07:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  等下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:07:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.01,0:07:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這麼多的話  就還能再戰上一段時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那輛巴士等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.69,0:08:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  司機先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.93,0:08:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  小氣鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是在逗我玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.27,0:09:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是叫諾艾爾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.58,0:09:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.68,0:09:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有很多事情想問妳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.48,0:09:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾也有很多話要跟乃乃香說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  為什麼妳會在我的房間裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.33,0:09:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為想見乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.57,0:09:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然一直在那個地方等著  但等不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.20,0:09:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾和乃乃香相遇的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.36,0:09:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.09,0:09:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我總覺得認識妳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.10,0:09:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們在一起過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:09:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.09,0:10:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很久很久以前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.96,0:10:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.45,0:10:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓嗎  我去買點東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾也要跟乃乃香一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.08,0:10:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很快就回來  等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.24,0:10:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等妳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香是因為太忙了沒時間陪我聊天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.89,0:11:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下哦  我很快就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.46,0:11:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等妳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還回來幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.12,0:11:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.69,0:11:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說我？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.87,0:11:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾  加油！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  果然不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.56,0:12:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.81,0:12:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心砰砰直跳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.39,0:13:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.96,0:13:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經很晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須在雪積起來之前回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.28,0:13:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.73,0:13:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.34,0:13:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.33,0:13:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.74,0:13:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要搬家了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.24,0:13:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.38,0:14:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.93,0:14:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已經回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.04,0:14:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.68,0:14:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.75,0:14:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來  乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.25,0:14:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.67,0:14:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得乃乃香會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.59,0:14:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.66,0:14:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道妳是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.33,0:14:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要再出現在我面前了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.64,0:15:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.15,0:15:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是不好意思啊  突然就出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.96,0:15:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.81,0:15:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.65,0:15:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  對不起  我不小心…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.74,0:16:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  妳已經發現了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.11,0:16:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.13,0:16:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在東京收拾行李的時候  一沒留神就搞壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.51,0:16:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來想在被妳發現之前更換的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.15,0:16:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以下班之後就買來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.56,0:16:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.69,0:16:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.85,0:16:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬上就要黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須要去道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.11,0:16:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須要向諾艾爾好好道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.52,0:16:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾  諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾  諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.59,0:17:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.07,0:17:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.07,0:17:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.94,0:17:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我不是來買東西的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.03,0:17:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找人  是個體型嬌小的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她迷路了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.65,0:17:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  並不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳認識一個叫諾艾爾的孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.26,0:17:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個穿著有點奇怪的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.23,0:17:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外國人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.34,0:17:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能找得到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要再出現在我面前了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.20,0:17:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…我會說出那種話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天文臺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.48,0:18:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.08,0:18:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我媽媽更厲害喲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是媽媽教我唱的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.93,0:18:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比乃乃香還厲害嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.55,0:18:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.04,0:18:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾也想聽聽妳媽媽的歌聲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和媽媽今天都要離開這座小鎮了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是要搬去東京
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.28,0:18:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去遠方了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.77,0:18:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  我把媽媽叫過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.97,0:18:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽了諾艾爾的事  她肯定馬上就會過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.98,0:18:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下哦  我很快就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.57,0:19:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我等妳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳去哪兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.65,0:19:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  諾艾爾還在等著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.72,0:19:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  我還沒有和大家好好告別
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要留出坐渡輪的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.42,0:19:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓妳媽媽為難
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會馬上回到這座小鎮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.59,0:19:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一家三口會一起回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.19,0:21:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.73,0:21:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直相信著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信著妳會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.95,0:21:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.73,0:21:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.26,0:21:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.61,0:21:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.37,0:21:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.26,0:21:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.88,0:21:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.76,0:21:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了  諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.75,0:21:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.72,0:21:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次輪到諾艾爾來實現約定了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.89,0:21:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約定？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.31,0:21:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  諾艾爾就是為了這個才在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.37,0:22:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了實現妳的願望
